data.description: Welcome to the country!  This great home sits on almost 2.5 acres in Stonewall!  This is a rare find.  Beautiful wooded lot with no backyard neighbors.  This is a 4 bedroom and 2 bath home that has been well maintained.  Large walk in closets in every room and a large walk in pantry!  TONS OF STORAGE! The backyard is great for entertaining with a nice concrete pad for your dining table, chairs and grill.  Large fenced back yard.  There is also a 20 x 20 shop on a concrete pad with a roll top door and electricity!  This home won't last long. It is in the coveted North Desoto school district.
